Bracket"> </span>1<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 33-2" id="2" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱتَّبِعْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And follow</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">what</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُوحَىٰٓ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">is inspired</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَيْكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">from</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَّبِّكَ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">your Lord.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَانَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">is</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">of what</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَعْمَلُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you do</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">خَبِيرًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">All-Aware.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>2<span class="icon rightBracket"> </s