 first rtl" dir="rtl">مِنْهُنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[of them]</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أُمَّهَـٰتِكُمْ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(as) your mothers.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">جَعَلَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">He has made</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَدْعِيَآءَكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">your adopted sons</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَبْنَآءَكُمْ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">your sons.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ذَٲلِكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">That</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَوْلُكُم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) your saying</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِأَفْوَٲهِكُمْ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">by your mouths,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱللَّهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">but Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَقُولُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">says</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْحَقَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the truth,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَهُوَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and He</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَهْدِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">guides</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلسَّبِيلَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(to) the Way.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>4<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 33-5" id="5" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱدْعُوهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Call them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِأَبَآئِهِمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">by their fathers;</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">هُوَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">it</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَقْسَطُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) more just</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عِندَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">near</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهِ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَإِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">But if</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَّمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَعْلَمُوٓاْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you know</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ءَابَآءَهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">their fathers -</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَإِخْوَٲنُكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">then (they are) your brothers</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText to