<p class="ayah 33-9" id="9" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَـٰٓأَيُّهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">O you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ءَامَنُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">believe!</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱذْكُرُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Remember</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">نِعْمَةَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(the) Favor</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَيْكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">upon you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِذْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">when</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">جَآءَتْكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">came to you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">جُنُودٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(the) hosts</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَأَرْسَلْنَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and We sent</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَيْهِمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">upon them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top firs