<p class="ayah 33-21" id="21" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَّقَدْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Certainly,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَانَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">is</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَسُولِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(the) Messenger</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أُسْوَةٌ حَسَنَةٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">an excellent example</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِّمَن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for (one) who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَانَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">has</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَرْجُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">hope</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(in) Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱلْيَوْمَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and the Day</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="r