<p class="ayah 33-36" id="36" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَانَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(it) is</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِمُؤْمِنٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for a believing man</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مُؤْمِنَةٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(for) a believing woman,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِذَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">when</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَضَى ٱللَّهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah has decided</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَرَسُولُهُۥٓ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and His Messenger</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَمْرًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a matter</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">that</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَكُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(there) should be</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَهُمُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar 