<p class="ayah 33-37" id="37" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَإِذْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And when</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَقُولُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you said</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِلَّذِىٓ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to the one,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَنْعَمَ ٱللَّهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah bestowed favor</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَيْهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">on him</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَأَنْعَمْتَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and you bestowed favor</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَيْهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">on him,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَمْسِكْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`Keep</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَيْكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to yourself</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">زَوْجَكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">your wife</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱتَّقِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and fear</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah.`</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَتُخْفِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">But you concealed</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">within</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">نَفْسِكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">yourself</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">what</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مُبْدِيهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(was to) disclose.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَتَخْشَى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And you fear</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلنَّاسَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the people,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱللَّهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">while Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَحَقُّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">has more right</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">that</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَخْشَـٰهُۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you (should) fear Him.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَلَمَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">So when</span><