<p class="ayah 33-45" id="45" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَـٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلنَّبِىُّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">O Prophet!</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed, We</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَرْسَلْنَـٰكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">have sent you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">شَـٰهِدًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(as) a witness</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَمُبَشِّرًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and a bearer of glad tidings</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَنَذِيرًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and (as) a warner</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>45<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
