></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱمْرَأَةً</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and a woman</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مُّؤْمِنَةً</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">believing</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">if</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَهَبَتْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">she gives</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">نَفْسَهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">herself</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِلنَّبِىِّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to the Prophet</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">if</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَرَادَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">wishes</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلنَّبِىُّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the Prophet</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَسْتَنكِحَهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">marry her -</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">خَالِصَةً</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">only</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَّكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for you,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِن دُونِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">excluding</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْمُؤْمِنِينَۗ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the believers.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَدْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Certainly,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلِمْنَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">We know</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">what</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَرَضْنَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">We have made obligatory</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَيْهِمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">upon them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِىٓ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">concerning</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَزْوَٲجِهِمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">their wives</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and whom</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَلَكَتْ أَيْمَـٰنُهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they rightfully possess,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِكَيْلَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">that not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَكُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">should be</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَيْكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">on you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">حَرَجٌۗ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">any discomfort.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَكَانَ ٱللَّهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And Allah is</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">غَفُورًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Oft-Forgiving,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَّحِيمًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Most Merciful</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>50<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 33-51" id="51" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">۞ تُرْجِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">You may defer</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">whom</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَشَآءُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you will</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِنْهُنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">of them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَتُــْٔوِىٓ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">or you may take</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَيْكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to yourself</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">whom</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَشَآءُۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you will.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَمَنِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And whoever</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱبْتَغَيْتَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you desire</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِمَّنْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">of those whom</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَزَلْتَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you (had) set aside -</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَلَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">then (there is) no</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">جُنَاحَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">blame</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَيْكَۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">upon you.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ذَٲلِكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">That</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَدْنَىٰٓ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) more suitable</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">that</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَقَرَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">may be cooled</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَعْيُنُهُنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">their eyes</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَحْزَنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they grieve</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَيَرْضَيْنَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and they may be pleased</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِمَآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">with what</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ءَاتَيْتَهُنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you have giv